# Product Catalog
## Softuni assignment for "Software Technologies" course (C#)

![home page](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/shturm/softuni-software-technologies-assignment/master/homescreenshot.png)

![overview](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/shturm/softuni-software-technologies-assignment/master/overview.png)
## Notable Features
#### Total man-days: 2+2+9 = 13 days
### Client
#### 2 days
- Angular 2
- RxJS (Reactive Extensions)
- SystemJs
- NodeJS
- Authorization aware routing


### Backend
#### 2 days
#### Fork of _100% authored_ code for Mono (linux) hosted compatible ASP.NET WebApi 2 application. Check commit log: [https://github.com/shturm/mono-webapi](https://github.com/shturm/mono-webapi). Implementation time = 9 days
- Mono compatible (.NET on Linux)
- Domain Driven Design
- ASP.NET MVC WebApi 2
- ORM: NHibernate (MySQL)

- ASP.NET Identity Framework v2
	- Role based authentication + authorization
	- `UserManager`, `RoleStore`, `UserStore` custom implemented for MySQL compatibility

	- OAuth 2.0 Bearer token authentication
